{"id":286768,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-公民维权日约700名上访维权人士聚集国/","date":"2013-03-30T05:31:05Z","modified":"2013-03-30T05:31:05Z","title":"维权网 | “公民维权日”约700名上访维权人士聚集国家信访局（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>星期五，是全国各地的上访维权者首个“公民维权日”。约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">700</span><span>名来自全国各地的访民聚集到位于北京西城区永定门内西街甲</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>号的中共中央办公厅人民来访接待室（国家信访局）向国办集访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>近年来，因各级信访工作机构接到信访人的信访事项后信访不作为，不依据《信访条例》办事；不出具信访事项受理凭证、不告知受理或者不受理。因此此次大约有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">400</span><span>名访民集体签名向国办递交了要求国务院信访工作机构依《信访条例》办事，查明事实，敦促各级信访工作机构出具信访事项受理凭证、告知受理与否。每个月最后一周的周五是上海访民集访国办的日子，这个习惯在上海访民中已经形成不成文的规定长达近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>年之久。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当天下午两点，按照惯例约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>多名上海访民和来自全国各地的访民（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">700</span><span>人左右）一起不约而同的汇集到被访民称为“三骗胡同”的国办信访接待室。其中大约有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">400</span><span>人参与了集体签名，向国办递交要求国务院信访工作机构及各级信访工作机构依《信访条例》办事，出具信访事项受理凭证、告知受理与否。并决定以后每个月最后一个星期五下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点，作为“公民维权日”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>有人印制了“小广告”，在访民中传阅，上书：“公民维权日”，地址：西城区永定门内西街甲</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>号；乘车路线：北京站乘坐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>路公交到永定门西下车即是。北京南站乘坐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">102</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">106</span><span>路公交到陶然桥北下车即是。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-z2TMl9E_tiI/UVZVmvyiz0I/AAAAAAAAfhI/p7z06Fjl-7w/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-z2TMl9E_tiI/UVZVmvyiz0I/AAAAAAAAfhI/p7z06Fjl-7w/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"260\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>“公民维权日”宣传卡</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-1tIIVThqTWM/UVZVmglInCI/AAAAAAAAfhQ/P2FmWd5Us10/s1600/51.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-1tIIVThqTWM/UVZVmglInCI/AAAAAAAAfhQ/P2FmWd5Us10/s320/51.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AoepY3LERO4/UVZVpvb0SuI/AAAAAAAAfhY/A9R8JOt2tb4/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"211\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AoepY3LERO4/UVZVpvb0SuI/AAAAAAAAfhY/A9R8JOt2tb4/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>约<span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span>米左右的国办胡同内挤满了等候登记接待的访民</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5Dof1YnxI6Q/UVZVq27prfI/AAAAAAAAfhg/lqmgUsSWunQ/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5Dof1YnxI6Q/UVZVq27prfI/AAAAAAAAfhg/lqmgUsSWunQ/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-q_WvEd3mpFw/UVZVuHdhfXI/AAAAAAAAfho/n_xryhZ_fCg/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"218\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-q_WvEd3mpFw/UVZVuHdhfXI/AAAAAAAAfho/n_xryhZ_fCg/s320/4.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>被挡在登记处门外的访民高呼口号“打倒腐败，还我人权！”抗议信访部门不作为</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<